 the media query style.\n\n\nAdding an !important to the media query fixes this.", "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/pull/1653#discussion_r442086323", "createdAt": "2020-06-18T09:15:21Z", "author": {"login": "schultek"}, "path": "src/main/webapp/app/shared/resizeable-container/resizeable-container.component.scss", "diffHunk": "@@ -97,3 +98,28 @@\n         padding-left: 5px;\n     }\n }\n+// for smaller screens (tablets, phones)\n+@media (max-width: 991.98px) {\n+    :host {\n+        flex-flow: column-reverse;\n+    }\n+\n+    .expanded {\n+        width: 100%;", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "9cee56cf63444ada3fa2e71018f3d85709311d40"}, "originalPosition": 19}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDMzMTg2MjIy", "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/pull/1653#pullrequestreview-433186222", "createdAt": "2020-06-18T11:23:03Z", "commit": {"oid": "9cee56cf63444ada3fa2e71018f3d85709311d40"}, "state": "CHANGES_REQUESTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 0, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": null, "endCursor": null, "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": []}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "0d81bc874d361eaeffe86bc5bb58dcf14bad0189", "author": {"user": {"login": "fde312", "name": "Francisco De las Casas Young"}}, "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/commit/0d81bc874d361eaeffe86bc5bb58dcf14bad0189", "committedDate": "2020-06-18T12:00:13Z", "message": "Update src/main/webapp/app/shared/resizeable-container/resizeable-container.component.scss\n\nCo-authored-by: Kilian Schulte <schultek@in.tum.de>"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "29dd7442ba1f3ba7b38fb00121cfd99f91533a6e", "author": {"user": null}, "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/commit/29dd7442ba1f3ba7b38fb00121cfd99f91533a6e", "committedDate": "2020-06-19T06:11:38Z", "message": "removed border, padding and left header for exercise participation and added z-index for